## Ansible - Mut-Node Nginx Setup 
- name: Setup Nginx on multiple nodes 
  host: all
  become: yes
  tasks:
    - name: Install nginx
      yum:
        name: nginx
        state: present

    - name: Start nginx service
        name: nginx
         state: started
